  characterName: Null
  characterPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f36fbf6dee429ca41a4cab3318474059, type: 3}
  lines:
  - First day. I made it.
  - This town is not right. Not right at all.
  - A smell that makes you gag is oozing from every corner.
  - But the lake... the stench coming from there is even undescribable.
  - But my cut was huge. I made lots of money. I must push forward for my family.
  textSpeed: 30
  typingSound: {fileID: 8300000, guid: f5d143911732a1f43b570748ed2458a4, type: 3}
